(1655, 102, 'about_intro', '<p class="emphasise">Miriam Grice is a highly skilled Semi Permanent Makeup Artist and has been involved in the beauty industry and performed permanent makeup treatments for over 10 years.</p>\r\nShe has trained with some of the leading companies from around the world, Biotek, Elite Training Academy, Finishing Touches, Dermace - who supply permanent makeup to the most prestigious clinics in the Country, Harley Street, Harrods, Selfridges etc.\r\n\r\nHer passion for precision and artistry is second to none. Miriam consistently creates permanent makeup that enhances and improves facial features. Her clients see how her high standard of work can renew and improve their look and image, which is why they have absolute confidence and peace of mind and continue to return to Miriam, and recommend her to others. Miriam also mentors and trains other permanent makeup artists in the industry as her decade of experience and natural artistic ability is widely recognised.'),
(1656, 102, '_about_intro', 'field_5457607245cf3'),
(1657, 10, 'about_intro', '<p class="emphasise">Miriam Grice is a highly skilled Semi Permanent Makeup Artist and has been involved in the beauty industry and performed permanent makeup treatments for over 10 years.</p>\r\nShe has trained with some of the leading companies from around the world, Biotek, Elite Training Academy, Finishing Touches, Dermace - who supply permanent makeup to the most prestigious clinics in the Country, Harley Street, Harrods, Selfridges etc.\r\n\r\nHer passion for precision and artistry is second to none. Miriam consistently creates permanent makeup that enhances and improves facial features. Her clients see how her high standard of work can renew and improve their look and image, which is why they have absolute confidence and peace of mind and continue to return to Miriam, and recommend her to others. Miriam also mentors and trains other permanent makeup artists in the industry as her decade of experience and natural artistic ability is widely recognised.'),
(1658, 10, '_about_intro', 'field_5457607245cf3'),
