(1905, 125, 'testimonial_0_review', 'Very friendly salon greeted with smiles n a hot drink very clean. Love my new brows defo have the wow factor I wanted. Miriam knew exactly what I wanted defo recommend her to my friends and clients thankyou Miriam x'),
(1906, 125, '_testimonial_0_review', 'field_545769d063d1b'),
(1907, 125, 'testimonial_0_client', 'Bal Hairdresser'),
(1908, 125, '_testimonial_0_client', 'field_545769da63d1c'),
(1909, 125, 'testimonial_1_review', 'Miriam, thank you so much for my perfect eyebrows! I''ve just been staring at them since I got home!! Even my husband commented on then saying how good they looked. Can''t wait to get my full face of make up on with my eyelashes on sat night to show them off!!'),
(1910, 125, '_testimonial_1_review', 'field_545769d063d1b'),
(1911, 125, 'testimonial_1_client', 'Katie Nicolaou'),
(1912, 125, '_testimonial_1_client', 'field_545769da63d1c'),
(1913, 125, 'testimonial_2_review', 'Wow!!! I had my brows done today and never been so happy in my life was well worth the journey amazing at what you do and so welcoming and lovely thank you the best money I''ve ever spent!'),
(1914, 125, '_testimonial_2_review', 'field_545769d063d1b'),
(1915, 125, 'testimonial_2_client', 'Lauren Boyles'),
(1916, 125, '_testimonial_2_client', 'field_545769da63d1c'),
(1917, 125, 'testimonial_3_review', 'Absolutely amazing. When having something so important and delicate done on your face I 100% recommend this diamond of a lady. Getting the perfect brow shape has always been my hardest task , so I knew when I decided to have them tattooed , that I needed someone who was an expert in their field. After friends have recommended Miriam I finally took the plunge and haven''t looked back! I am so thrilled with my brows . Working as a photographer means I usually had finished work to realise one of my brows was rubbed off! NOT NO MORE!! Perfect shape (which I could never achieve) and so lovely I always get complimented on them. Thank you Miriam , I can''t wait to come back for more xxxxxxxx'),
(1918, 125, '_testimonial_3_review', 'field_545769d063d1b'),
(1919, 125, 'testimonial_3_client', 'Lauren-Chypree Holmes'),
(1920, 125, '_testimonial_3_client', 'field_545769da63d1c'),
(1921, 125, 'testimonial_4_review', 'Thank you for making my lips more symmetrical I’m really happy with them. I have always had a complex about my lips being abit thin and misshaped, after the liner and blush treatment they are more defined but still natural.'),
(1922, 125, '_testimonial_4_review', 'field_545769d063d1b'),
(1923, 125, 'testimonial_4_client', 'Jenny W'),
(1924, 125, '_testimonial_4_client', 'field_545769da63d1c'),
(1925, 125, 'testimonial_5_review', 'I love my eyeliner, its so neat and crisp and obviously stays put all day. I also like the fact that when I wake up with no other makeup on I look good, its not too prominent to look too much – perfect , thank you. X.'),
(1926, 125, '_testimonial_5_review', 'field_545769d063d1b'),
(1927, 125, 'testimonial_5_client', 'Stacey r'),
