(2188, 8, 'banner_intro', '<blockquote class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 center-col-block">Semi Permanent Makeup or cosmetic tattooing is one of the beauty industries</blockquote>'),
(2189, 8, '_banner_intro', 'field_545a4bd5d2aa6'),
(2190, 8, 'intro', '<p class="text-center introduction">View the case studies below to see what each of the treatments Miriam offer involves. All of the case studies are of real clients that have recently been to the salon.</p>'),
(2191, 8, '_intro', 'field_545a4c00e00f0'),
(2192, 8, 'before_title', 'Before the Treatment'),
(2193, 8, '_before_title', 'field_545a4c27e00f3'),
(2194, 8, 'before_copy', 'I was really nervous before the treatment as I just couldn''t imagine what the finished effect would look like. All of Miriam''s pictures looked amazing so she was the only person I would trust to do my brows. She applied anaesthetic cream whilst we went through the consultation and we discussed what styles I liked.\r\n\r\nShe showed me lots of pictures, and advised me as to the right thickness and styles that would suit me. I showed her my favourite pictures from her portfolio and she tailored the same styles to suit me. Miriam drew the design in pencil for me to see first and even then I could see straight away how much better it looked!'),
(2195, 8, '_before_copy', 'field_545a4c3ce00f4'),
(2196, 8, 'before_image', '142'),
(2197, 8, '_before_image', 'field_545a4c78e00f5'),
(2198, 8, 'during_title', 'During the Treatment'),
(2199, 8, '_during_title', 'field_545a4caa1776b'),
(2200, 8, 'during_copy', 'Once we had agreed on the shape and colour choice I wasn''t as nervous. Miriam was very reassuring and made me feel really comfortable. The actual tattooing didn''t hurt, it was the tweezing and threading beforehand that caused me more discomfort, the numbing cream worked a treat. As soon as I looked in the mirror when we''d finished I was amazed, they were just brilliant!'),
(2201, 8, '_during_copy', 'field_545a4ccd1776c'),
(2202, 8, 'during_image', '143'),
(2203, 8, '_during_image', 'field_545a4cda1776d'),
(2204, 8, 'after_title', 'After the Treatment'),
(2205, 8, '_after_title', 'field_545a4d0dc1d61'),
(2206, 8, 'after_copy', 'I was really nervous before the treatment as I just couldn''t imagine what the finished effect would look like. All of Miriam''s pictures looked amazing so she was the only person I would trust to do my brows. She applied anaesthetic cream whilst we went through the consultation and we discussed what styles I liked.\r\n\r\nShe showed me lots of pictures, and advised me as to the right thickness and styles that would suit me. I showed her my favourite pictures from her portfolio and she tailored the same styles to suit me. Miriam drew the design in pencil for me to see first and even then I could see straight away how much better it looked!'),
(2207, 8, '_after_copy', 'field_545a4d18c1d62'),
(2208, 8, 'after_image', '144'),
(2209, 8, '_after_image', 'field_545a4d23c1d63'),
