(2221, 8, 'cta_title', 'A FEW WEEKS AFTER THE TREATMENT'),
(2222, 8, '_cta_title', 'field_545f70e9c1377'),
(2223, 8, 'cta_copy', 'A few weeks after the treatment I booked a model photoshoot and I am so pleased with the results.  Not having to draw my eyebrows on everyday is amazing. I would highly reccomend to anyone.'),
(2224, 8, '_cta_copy', 'field_545f7100c1378'),
