(1, 1, '2011-09-18 16:19:37', '2011-09-18 15:19:37', 'I have to say the bottom line is personal preference with any brow design.  Thicker more “natural” brows or “HD” brows are very popular these days, and looking at Keira Knightley I have to join the band wagon.  Although thinner brows do give a lifting effect to the eye area and almost elongate the face – the thicker brow does give a more youthful and unaffected appearance.\r\n\r\nIf I were to give Keira Knightley a simple eyebrow shape I would be tempted to take a few hairs away underneath to accentuate the arch.  As the face of <strong><em>Chanel Mademoiselle</em></strong>  Keira Knightley exudes sophistication and has the perfect look to match the image.', 'Keira Knightley – Thick or Thin?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'keira-knightley-thick-or-thin', '', '', '2014-09-20 05:50:26', '2014-09-20 04:50:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/miriam/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 1),
